    {
      "id": "PopularPost119118",
      "post_content": "Part of yet another cycle! This time it was 5 common enchantments that all had flash - the others are [\u00c6ther Web](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=\u00c6ther Web), [Feebleness](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Feebleness),[Ghitu Firebreathing](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ghitu Firebreathing) and [Temporal Isolation](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Temporal Isolation).\n  \n   \nRight now, community rating has Ophidian Eye in the middle of the pack, and I think that's justified. Comparing this to [Sleeper's Robe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleeper's Robe) is fair in some cases, but keep in mind that the robe specifies \"combat damage\" while this one triggers off anything. It's what makes hyrule's combo work so effectively, and you could also put it on something like [Plague Spitter](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Spitter), [Jaya Ballard, Task Mage](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jaya Ballard, Task Mage) or [Kumano, Master Yamabushi](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kumano, Master Yamabushi). Hell, even [Squallmonger](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squallmonger) would work in a multiplayer situation. ",
      "posted_by": "Leshrac_Nightwalker",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost119118\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Part of yet another cycle!  This time it was 5 common enchantments that all had flash - the others are <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"\u00c6ther Web\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=\u00c6ther Web\">\u00c6ther Web</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Feebleness\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Feebleness\">Feebleness</a>,<a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ghitu Firebreathing\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ghitu Firebreathing\">Ghitu Firebreathing</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Temporal Isolation\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Temporal Isolation\">Temporal Isolation</a>.  \r<br/> <br/>Right now, community rating has Ophidian Eye in the middle of the pack, and I think that's justified.  Comparing this to <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Sleeper's Robe\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleeper's Robe\">Sleeper's Robe</a> is fair in some cases, but keep in mind that the robe specifies \"combat damage\" while this one triggers off anything.  It's what makes hyrule's combo work so effectively, and you could also put it on something like <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Plague Spitter\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Plague Spitter\">Plague Spitter</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Jaya Ballard, Task Mage\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Jaya Ballard, Task Mage\">Jaya Ballard, Task Mage</a> or <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Kumano, Master Yamabushi\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Kumano, Master Yamabushi\">Kumano, Master Yamabushi</a>.  Hell, even <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Squallmonger\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Squallmonger\">Squallmonger</a> would work in a multiplayer situation.  </span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '119118'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2435\">Leshrac_Nightwalker</span>\r\n                                (11/30/2010 11:30:35 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
