      "id": "PopularPost57571",
      "post_content": "While the flash can allow you to get away with some mid-combat shenanigans, and I always like when they make an aura that turns its bearer into a famous critter, in this case [Ophidian](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ophidian), I truly feel that [Sleeper's Robe](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sleeper's Robe) is overall a better deal.  \n  \nReally cool art though.",
