      "id": "PopularPost2311",
      "post_content": "Flash increased [the card](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curiosity)'s cost by ![2](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=2&type=symbol) like a cantrip normally does...  \nAlthough you can get an instant advantage from flash in this case, the increasement is still a bit much, isn't it?  \nBut the name with [its reference](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ophidian) and the artwork is awesome!   \nI'd like to see this effect as a keyword ability by the way...",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost2311\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_post\">Flash increased <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Curiosity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Curiosity\">the card</a>'s cost by <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"2\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=2&amp;type=symbol\"/> like a cantrip normally does...<br/>Although you can get an instant advantage from flash in this case, the increasement is still a bit much, isn't it?<br/>But the name with <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ophidian\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ophidian\">its reference</a> and the artwork is awesome! <br/>I'd like to see this effect as a keyword ability by the way...</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '2311'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (2/22/2009 12:29:31 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postRating_starRa